        "content": "<p>cuiweixie opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12843\">PR #12843</a> from <code>cuiweixie:fix/pulley-xdiv32u-trap-opcode</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h2>Summary</h2>\n<p>Fix a copy-paste bug in the Pulley interpreter: <code>xdiv32_u</code> reported divide-by-zero traps with the wrong opcode type parameter (<code>XDiv64U</code> instead of <code>XDiv32U</code>).</p>\n<h2>Testing</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Change is a one-line opcode fix aligned with <code>xdiv64_u</code> and other 32-bit ops; no behavioral change to trapping itself beyond correct trap metadata.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
